

{"id":932,"date":"2022-02-16T09:19:46","date_gmt":"2022-02-16T08:19:46","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/10.1.1.190\/?page_id=932"},"modified":"2024-06-25T21:06:21","modified_gmt":"2024-06-25T20:06:21","slug":"ingeniorat","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/ingeniorat\/","title":{"rendered":"Ing\u00e9niorat"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ing\u00e9nieur en Informatique (Nouveau Syst\u00e8me)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>L&#8217;universit\u00e9 USTHB et la facult\u00e9 d&#8217;Informatique ont d\u00e9marr\u00e9 \u00e0 nouveau la formation des ing\u00e9nieurs en Informatique au titre de l&#8217;ann\u00e9e universitaire 2022\/2023. Ci-dessous se trouve la r\u00e9partition des modules ainsi que le programme des enseignements des deux premi\u00e8res ann\u00e9es (D&#8217;\u00e9cole pr\u00e9paratoire).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-huge-font-size\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#e60b0b\" class=\"has-inline-color\">mise \u00e0 jour  le 04\/09\/2023<\/mark><\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Fichier<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>T\u00e9l\u00e9charger<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Nouveau programme d\u00e9taill\u00e9 appliqu\u00e9<strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#f00a0a\" class=\"has-inline-color\"> \u00e0 partir de l&#8217;ann\u00e9e 2023\/2024<\/mark><\/strong><\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/Canevas-Offre-de-formation-TC-ingenieur_Mai-1.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/Canevas-Offre-de-formation-TC-ingenieur_Mai-1.pdf\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"52\" height=\"52\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1417\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/icons8-pdf-100.png\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Programme d\u00e9taill\u00e9 par mati\u00e8re des enseignements <strong><mark style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#d40b0b\" class=\"has-inline-color\">(Appliqu\u00e9 durant l&#8217;ann\u00e9e 2022\/2023)<\/mark><\/strong><\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/programme-modules-ING-Informatique-recu-2022.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/programme-modules-ING-Informatique-recu-2022.pdf\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"52\" height=\"52\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1417\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/icons8-pdf-100.png\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>R\u00e9partition des modules et Arr\u00e9t\u00e9 MI n\u00b0060 du 15 janvier 2023<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Arrete-MI-n\u00b0060-du-15-janvier-2023-modifiant-larrete-n\u00b01399-du-22-octobre-2022.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Arrete-MI-n\u00b0060-du-15-janvier-2023-modifiant-larrete-n\u00b01399-du-22-octobre-2022.pdf\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"52\" height=\"52\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1417\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/icons8-pdf-100.png\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Ing\u00e9nieur en Informatique (Ancien Syst\u00e8me)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Cette formation d\u2019ingenieur , sur 05 ann\u00e9es, a une double finalit\u00e9 :<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Professionnelle pour permettre aux dipl\u00f4m\u00e9s d\u2019\u00eatre imm\u00e9diatement op\u00e9rationnels sur le march\u00e9 de l\u2019emploi.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Th\u00e9orique pour leur permettre d\u2019acqu\u00e9rir les fondements th\u00e9oriques pour une poursuite des \u00e9tudes.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Ainsi, l\u2019informaticien se doit de poss\u00e9der une base de connaissance qui lui permettra de s\u2019adapter \u00e0 toutes les innovations technologiques et de recherche. Ces connaissances fondamentales concernent les domaines cl\u00e9s tels que : l\u2019architecture des ordinateurs, les syst\u00e8mes d\u2019exploitation, les r\u00e9seaux, les BDD, &#8230; . En 5\u00e8me Ann\u00e9e, l\u2019\u00e9tudiant pr\u00e9pare un projet de fin d\u2019\u00e9tudes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Fichier<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>T\u00e9l\u00e9charger<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Programme d&#8217;ing\u00e9nieur en informatique (ancien syst\u00e8me)<\/td><td><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Programme-Ingenieur-en-Informatique.pdf\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/Programme-Ingenieur-en-Informatique.pdf\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"52\" height=\"52\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1417\" src=\"http:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/icons8-pdf-100.png\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ing\u00e9nieur en Informatique (Nouveau Syst\u00e8me) L&#8217;universit\u00e9 USTHB et la facult\u00e9 d&#8217;Informatique ont d\u00e9marr\u00e9 \u00e0 nouveau la formation des ing\u00e9nieurs en <span class=\"readmore\"><a href=\"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/ingeniorat\/\">Suite<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-932","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/932"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/finfo.usthb.dz\/index.php\/wp-